#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/index.rst:3
msgid "Module: Spatial Database Concepts with PostGIS / PostgreSQL"
msgstr "Modul: Koncepti prostornih baza podataka sa PostGIS / PostgreSQL"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/index.rst:5
msgid ""
"Spatial Databases allow the storage of the geometries of records inside a "
"Database as well as providing functionality for querying and retrieving the "
"records using these Geometries. In this module we will use PostGIS, an "
"extension to PostgreSQL, to learn how to setup a spatial database, import "
"data into the database and make use of the geographic functions that PostGIS"
" offers."
msgstr ""
"Prostorne baze podataka omogućavaju skladištenje geometrija zapisa unutar "
"baze podataka, kao i pružanje funkcionalnosti za upite i preuzimanje zapisa "
"pomoću ovih geometrija. U ovom modulu ćemo koristiti PostGIS, proširenje "
"PostgreSQL-a, da bismo naučili kako da podesimo prostornu bazu podataka, "
"uvezemo podatke u bazu podataka i koristimo geografske funkcije koje PostGIS"
" nudi."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/index.rst:11
msgid ""
"While working through this section, you may want to keep a copy of the "
"**PostGIS cheat sheet**  available from `Boston GIS user group "
"<https://www.bostongis.com/postgis_quickguide.bqg>`_. Another useful "
"resource is the `online <https://postgis.net/documentation/>`_ PostGIS "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Dok radite na ovom odeljku, možda ćete želeti da sačuvate kopiju **PostGIS "
"špargalice** koja je dostupna od `Boston GIS korisničke grupe "
"<https://www.bostongis.com/postgis_quickguide.bqg>`_. Još jedan koristan "
"resurs je `onlajn <https://postgis.net/documentation/>`_ PostGIS "
"dokumentacija."

